item.name: Partially update a DataPoint for a Quest

variable.description: (Required) Id of Quest the DataPoint belongs to

request.description:
Sample request (this request updates the name and description) \
PATCH quests/questId/datapoints/dataPointId \
[ \
    { \
        "op": "replace", \
        "path": "/name", \
        "value": "NEWNAME" \
    }, \
    { \
        "op": "replace", \
        "path": "/description", \
        "value": "NEWDESCRIPTION" \
    } \
]
